Where $\gamma_{ij} = 1/\sqrt{1-\beta_{ij}^2}$ is the Lorentz-like factor.

The trivector $\Omega_{123} = v_1 \times_\Phi v_2 \times_\Phi v_3$ represents the oriented volume of the three-body configuration in 7D space.

